# Netlify response headers for all routes.
#
# Shopify embedded apps must be renderable inside Shopify admin's iframe.
# The app sets Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors dynamically via
# addDocumentResponseHeaders(), but we also strip any X-Frame-Options that
# Netlify or a dependency might inject, because X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
# would block the iframe regardless of the CSP header.
/*
  ! X-Frame-Options
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
